          h2 Color
          p The UI environment is demanding of colors that are less welcome in marketing materials. Yellows become browns for contrast and readability purposes. Hover states mean additional shaded / tinted versions of things. The product design color palette took the original marketing palette and filled in the gaps for performance in any situation.
      
      //- Desktop version
