        .default-text.round-top-xl
          h2 Typography
          p The goal of the type stack was to have a top end that was bold enough for marketing heros, and a bottom end that was robust enough for legal documents with multiple levels of headings. We borrowed an abstraction from bootstrap and extended the headings with two Display sizes that enhanced the h1 while keeping the h1s themselves at a sane size.

